| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3122 — Mass File Rename (underground)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ac663809-58c7-5022-abc8-404b835988e8"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
